m_lines: Hi, I'm going to make some great pixel-art for this game!
Me: Nice, can't wait to see it.
And then we can make a game on aliens injecting baby aliens in a peasant's stomach.
Me: Oh well, I'll have to think about that...
Me: Yeah, let's just focus on the dialogue system, will you.
Why? Nothing's more hearthwarming than baby aliens inside people.
Me: You're right, I'm already crying.
